#

Herb-Crusted Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$5.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 25%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide DishGourmet

Description

Creamy mashed potatoes infused with garlic and topped with a fragrant herb crust.

Ingredients

  • Russet potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Fresh chives: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
